### Get All Services
GET {{baseUrl}}/services

### Get My Services (Requires Authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/services/my-services
Authorization: Bearer {{token_prestador}}

### Get Services By Store ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/services/store/{{storeId}}

### Get Service By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}

### Update Service (Requires Authentication)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_prestador}}

{
  "title": "Corte de Cabelo Masculino Atualizado",
  "description": "Corte de cabelo moderno com técnicas profissionais e finalização premium",
  "price": 60.00,
  "durationMinutes": 35,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/new-service-image.jpg"
}

### Update Service - Partial Update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_prestador}}

{
  "price": 55.00
}

### Upload Image for Service (Requires Authentication)
### Use FormData with field name 'file'
POST {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}/upload-image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{token_prestador}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="service-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Delete Service (Requires Authentication)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token_prestador}}

